WEBVTT

00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:12.020 --> 00:01:15.140
[Episode 31]

00:01:17.390 --> 00:01:18.370
Have you found the compass?

00:01:25.670 --> 00:01:26.370
Great.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:30.650
Promise me.

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:34.250
Take our people back across the sea.

00:01:36.270 --> 00:01:37.220
You and Lifei

00:01:39.240 --> 00:01:41.370
Must live well.

00:01:43.390 --> 00:01:43.940
Alright.

00:02:10.910 --> 00:02:13.060
Mu has gone with Jiaping.

00:02:13.800 --> 00:02:17.340
We don't know how Lifei and the others are doing.

00:02:21.110 --> 00:02:21.620
Mr. Zuo,

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:24.130
I'm heading back to Duanming City now.

00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:25.810
If the mountain-sea barrier falls,

00:02:26.150 --> 00:02:27.570
Please look after the disciples

00:02:27.710 --> 00:02:28.940
Who've retreated inland

00:02:30.080 --> 00:02:32.620
And preserve one last hope for the immortal sects.

00:02:35.990 --> 00:02:36.570
Don't worry.

00:02:50.990 --> 00:02:52.780
The East Sea will witness a tough battle.

00:02:53.040 --> 00:02:53.810
We healers

00:02:54.040 --> 00:02:55.410
Are meant to save lives.

00:02:55.960 --> 00:02:57.300
If we don't go to the East Sea now,

00:02:57.670 --> 00:02:58.740
Then when will we?

00:02:59.080 --> 00:02:59.970
Let me pack.

00:03:00.430 --> 00:03:01.780
I'll go with you to Duanming City.

00:03:02.150 --> 00:03:02.650
Great!

00:03:02.900 --> 00:03:03.940
Let's go together!

00:03:09.590 --> 00:03:10.180
Take care.

00:03:10.990 --> 00:03:11.460
Take care.

00:03:12.150 --> 00:03:12.810
Both of you,

00:03:14.240 --> 00:03:14.780
Take care.

00:03:18.320 --> 00:03:20.940
Thanks to Prince Ying

00:03:20.960 --> 00:03:21.780
And Immortal Cuixuan's strategy,

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:23.370
We dealt Yecha a heavy blow.

00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:24.460
Otherwise,

00:03:24.870 --> 00:03:26.130
If the demons had taken the Divine Tree,

00:03:26.620 --> 00:03:27.740
It would have been a catastrophe.

00:03:28.590 --> 00:03:29.530
What a pity.

00:03:30.480 --> 00:03:33.220
Immortal Cuixuan fell into Yecha's hands.

00:03:33.900 --> 00:03:35.250
I've buried my master.

00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:37.970
He died fighting demons.

00:03:39.040 --> 00:03:40.130
He has no regrets.

00:03:42.590 --> 00:03:43.020
Everyone,

00:03:44.550 --> 00:03:46.410
I will dedicate myself to slaying demons

00:03:47.110 --> 00:03:48.300
And upholding my master's will.

00:03:48.760 --> 00:03:49.410
But

00:03:49.590 --> 00:03:50.340
The Divine Tree has let the Demon Lord

00:03:50.360 --> 00:03:51.620
Slip away time and again.

00:03:52.360 --> 00:03:53.300
She harbors ill intent.

00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:55.460
Keeping her around is a liability.

00:03:56.320 --> 00:03:56.970
I say

00:03:57.550 --> 00:03:58.940
The Divine Tree must be eliminated.

00:04:01.150 --> 00:04:02.900
Lifei must have been bewitched

00:04:02.920 --> 00:04:03.690
By the Demon Lord.

00:04:04.150 --> 00:04:04.940
I trust her.

00:04:05.240 --> 00:04:06.970
This isn't about trust.

00:04:07.670 --> 00:04:10.410
Duanming City can't afford another disaster.

00:04:10.870 --> 00:04:11.300
Exactly.

00:04:12.270 --> 00:04:13.130
The Sea Calamity is coming.

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:14.180
The demons covet her.

00:04:14.430 --> 00:04:15.650
If they come for her again...

00:04:15.670 --> 00:04:17.090
Lifei is my future wife.

00:04:17.870 --> 00:04:19.250
I'll keep a close watch on her.

00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:23.210
She won't fall into demon hands again.

00:04:46.680 --> 00:04:47.210
My Lord,

00:04:47.680 --> 00:04:49.330
Jiang Lifei is under house arrest by Ji Tongzhou.

00:04:49.710 --> 00:04:50.570
She's safe for now.

00:04:55.560 --> 00:04:56.620
This ancient text says

00:04:57.710 --> 00:04:58.890
That when the Sea Calamity comes,

00:04:59.440 --> 00:05:00.810
The seawater will surge backward into Guixu,

00:05:01.440 --> 00:05:02.540
Breaching the heavenly chasm.

00:05:03.030 --> 00:05:06.570
With this Xuantian Biluo Compass,

00:05:07.080 --> 00:05:09.740
We can find a way across the sea

00:05:10.760 --> 00:05:11.890
And cross Guixu.

00:05:13.390 --> 00:05:14.500
Cross Guixu?

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:16.860
Legend says Guixu can devour the heavens

00:05:16.880 --> 00:05:17.660
And has countless dark spirits.

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:18.980
How can anyone cross it?

00:05:19.790 --> 00:05:20.740
There's always a way.

00:05:26.640 --> 00:05:27.250
My Lord,

00:05:28.030 --> 00:05:29.010
Aren't you going to save Jiang Lifei?

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:33.420
I have my own duty to fulfill,

00:05:33.760 --> 00:05:34.980
And you do what you must.

00:05:38.230 --> 00:05:38.740
No need.

00:05:46.320 --> 00:05:49.940
We each have our own duties to fulfill.

00:06:05.710 --> 00:06:07.330
I had these pastries specially made.

00:06:12.200 --> 00:06:13.060
All your favorites.

00:06:14.320 --> 00:06:15.570
Why did you side with Cuixuan?

00:06:26.710 --> 00:06:27.570
The immortal sects are in decline.

00:06:28.150 --> 00:06:29.100
He's a senior master.

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:30.940
And he's willing to help me fight the demons.

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:33.540
Why shouldn't I work with him?

00:06:34.230 --> 00:06:35.210
He killed my master

00:06:35.230 --> 00:06:36.210
And Mr. Shen!

00:06:37.200 --> 00:06:38.180
He's monstrous.

00:06:38.200 --> 00:06:39.770
You won't end well working with him!

00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:46.250
Does doing everything for the greater good ever end well?

00:06:49.200 --> 00:06:49.860
My uncle,

00:06:50.440 --> 00:06:50.940
My brother,

00:06:51.560 --> 00:06:52.620
And your senior brothers and sisters.

00:06:53.520 --> 00:06:54.420
Did any of them get a good ending?

00:06:57.320 --> 00:06:58.300
If they knew

00:06:59.390 --> 00:07:00.210
This is what

00:07:00.590 --> 00:07:01.940
Their sacrifice bought,

00:07:03.320 --> 00:07:04.420
Do you think they'd rest

00:07:04.440 --> 00:07:05.180
In peace?

00:07:07.030 --> 00:07:08.180
They didn't do it

00:07:09.230 --> 00:07:10.740
For their own good endings.

00:07:11.470 --> 00:07:12.300
They did it for you,

00:07:12.880 --> 00:07:13.620
For me,

00:07:14.790 --> 00:07:16.690
And for everyone they died protecting.

00:07:18.640 --> 00:07:19.180
Tongzhou.

00:07:19.910 --> 00:07:20.810
Wrong is wrong.

00:07:21.440 --> 00:07:22.770
Nothing justifies it.

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:24.980
Cuixuan offered himself to the demons

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:26.130
For his ambition.

00:07:26.710 --> 00:07:27.300
And you?

00:07:28.640 --> 00:07:29.690
What were you fighting for

00:07:30.320 --> 00:07:31.250
All this way?

00:07:32.230 --> 00:07:33.130
Did you forget?

00:07:47.120 --> 00:07:47.890
What did I do wrong?

00:07:50.440 --> 00:07:51.130
I fight demons

00:07:51.150 --> 00:07:51.980
And protect the immortal sects.

00:07:52.560 --> 00:07:53.330
What did I do wrong?

00:07:54.390 --> 00:07:55.570
You're the one who's wrong!

00:07:56.830 --> 00:07:58.210
You chose to betray me

00:07:58.520 --> 00:07:59.570
And be with Lei Xiuyuan.

00:08:00.200 --> 00:08:01.300
The Divine Tree and Yecha.

00:08:02.080 --> 00:08:03.180
A thousand years

00:08:03.200 --> 00:08:04.370
Haven't changed a thing!

00:08:07.200 --> 00:08:08.010
What do you mean?

00:08:12.150 --> 00:08:13.330
This is my ancestor.

00:08:14.120 --> 00:08:15.370
I only recently found out

00:08:15.680 --> 00:08:16.570
That this scroll

00:08:16.760 --> 00:08:18.010
Records my ancestor's past.

00:08:18.760 --> 00:08:19.250
Turns out

00:08:19.880 --> 00:08:21.010
He loved the Divine Tree as well.

00:08:22.030 --> 00:08:23.370
But the Divine Tree abandoned him

00:08:23.710 --> 00:08:25.180
And fled with Yecha.

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:28.060
With the Divine Tree's power, Yecha

00:08:28.640 --> 00:08:29.500
Unleashed the Sea Calamity

00:08:29.520 --> 00:08:30.330
And overturned the Central Plains.

00:08:33.270 --> 00:08:34.810
My ancestor trained in Xuanhua Sacred Fire

00:08:35.120 --> 00:08:36.330
To protect the people.

00:08:37.230 --> 00:08:38.850
He led the immortal sects to quell the Sea Calamity.

00:08:39.400 --> 00:08:40.780
But his spirit power was depleted,

00:08:41.920 --> 00:08:42.570
And he died soon after.

00:08:44.200 --> 00:08:44.730
Lifei,

00:08:46.160 --> 00:08:47.610
Are you really going to make the same mistake?

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:57.420
That thousand-year-old record

00:08:57.750 --> 00:08:58.540
May not be true.

00:08:59.870 --> 00:09:00.570
I am me.

00:09:01.160 --> 00:09:01.970
The Divine Tree is the Divine Tree.

00:09:02.830 --> 00:09:04.210
I won't repeat the past.

00:09:04.750 --> 00:09:05.330
Besides,

00:09:06.160 --> 00:09:07.660
Xiuyuan isn't the Yecha from back then.

00:09:08.200 --> 00:09:10.020
He truly wants to help us withstand the Sea Calamity.

00:09:10.630 --> 00:09:11.940
Why are you still defending him?

00:09:20.660 --> 00:09:21.260
Lifei,

00:09:21.870 --> 00:09:23.380
Do you really need to see bloodshed again

00:09:24.320 --> 00:09:25.570
To realize you're wrong?

00:09:25.750 --> 00:09:26.780
You're the one who's wrong!

00:09:27.960 --> 00:09:29.020
The Sea Calamity is coming.

00:09:29.830 --> 00:09:31.330
Our enemy isn't the demons!

00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:33.540
We need to fight the Sea Calamity.

00:09:33.660 --> 00:09:34.940
Trust Xiuyuan.

00:09:35.510 --> 00:09:36.260
Trust me.

00:09:43.440 --> 00:09:44.490
Whether I trust you or not doesn't matter.

00:09:45.280 --> 00:09:45.970
In this life,

00:09:46.510 --> 00:09:47.850
I won't let Yecha take you away.

00:09:53.710 --> 00:09:54.330
Forget it.

00:09:55.510 --> 00:09:56.490
Nothing I say matters.

00:10:05.990 --> 00:10:06.940
Take your jade pendant back!

00:10:12.830 --> 00:10:13.900
I never take back

00:10:14.710 --> 00:10:15.730
What I give.

00:10:21.940 --> 00:10:22.420
Here.

00:10:22.830 --> 00:10:23.540
Eat something.

00:10:25.820 --> 00:10:26.300
Eat!

00:10:38.420 --> 00:10:39.570
Xingzheng Hall's restriction spell?

00:11:02.420 --> 00:11:02.970
Changyue.

00:11:03.560 --> 00:11:04.060
Gelin.

00:11:04.590 --> 00:11:06.610
We heard about you and Lifei's engagement

00:11:07.350 --> 00:11:08.300
And rushed over overnight.

00:11:08.870 --> 00:11:10.610
Didn't expect so much to have happened.

00:11:10.990 --> 00:11:12.330
A lot has happened indeed.

00:11:12.870 --> 00:11:13.970
You rushed over overnight.

00:11:14.180 --> 00:11:15.300
Why not settle in first?

00:11:15.420 --> 00:11:16.300
We can talk another day.

00:11:16.590 --> 00:11:17.210
Tongzhou,

00:11:17.820 --> 00:11:20.660
I heard Lifei's been locked in her room for days.

00:11:21.230 --> 00:11:22.020
How is she?

00:11:22.460 --> 00:11:23.210
We want to see her.

00:11:25.560 --> 00:11:26.540
She's my future wife.

00:11:26.940 --> 00:11:27.810
Of course she's fine.

00:11:28.350 --> 00:11:29.660
Then why are you keeping her in there

00:11:29.680 --> 00:11:30.690
With a restriction spell?

00:11:33.340 --> 00:11:34.970
Right now, both immortals and demons

00:11:35.470 --> 00:11:36.810
Are after Lifei's power.

00:11:38.060 --> 00:11:39.570
And she was wounded by Lei Xiuyuan.

00:11:40.220 --> 00:11:40.900
She's weak.

00:11:41.560 --> 00:11:42.260
Hard times

00:11:42.510 --> 00:11:43.850
Call for hard measures.

00:11:44.110 --> 00:11:45.420
Wounded by Xiuyuan?

00:11:49.940 --> 00:11:51.180
Lei Xiuyuan has fully fallen to the demon side.

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:53.020
He killed Mr. Shen,

00:11:53.510 --> 00:11:54.810
And when he couldn't take the Divine Tree,

00:11:55.560 --> 00:11:56.810
He struck Lifei.

00:11:57.560 --> 00:11:58.730
But we're not outsiders.

00:11:58.750 --> 00:11:59.730
Surely we can see Lifei.

00:12:05.470 --> 00:12:06.330
She just rested.

00:12:06.980 --> 00:12:07.690
Come back tomorrow

00:12:08.180 --> 00:12:08.810
After she wakes.

00:12:09.350 --> 00:12:09.810
Then we...

00:12:13.340 --> 00:12:13.780
Alright.

00:12:14.420 --> 00:12:15.300
We'll come tomorrow.

00:12:23.180 --> 00:12:24.850
What's Ji Tongzhou doing?

00:12:26.830 --> 00:12:28.730
I wonder how Lifei really is.

00:12:36.040 --> 00:12:37.730
I listened carefully to Lifei's heartbeat.

00:12:38.280 --> 00:12:39.020
She's not in danger.

00:12:39.630 --> 00:12:41.940
Guess Tongzhou hasn't been too harsh on her.

00:12:42.830 --> 00:12:44.180
We've known each other since we were young

00:12:44.920 --> 00:12:45.900
And share deep bonds.

00:12:46.750 --> 00:12:48.970
I trust Tongzhou will protect Lifei.

00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:50.140
Forget it.

00:12:50.660 --> 00:12:52.420
I actually wished them well.

00:12:52.830 --> 00:12:54.540
I never thought he'd collude with that snake Cuixuan

00:12:54.540 --> 00:12:55.210
And deceive Lifei.

00:12:56.320 --> 00:12:58.450
Cuixuan nearly devoured Lifei before.

00:13:00.040 --> 00:13:00.570
Alright.

00:13:01.470 --> 00:13:04.780
Duanming City's situation is complicated right now.

00:13:05.200 --> 00:13:07.060
Tongzhou has to stay fair

00:13:07.510 --> 00:13:08.380
And protect Lifei.

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:11.330
That's no easy task for him.

00:13:11.750 --> 00:13:14.090
Right now, the most important thing is the Sea Calamity.

00:13:15.280 --> 00:13:15.810
Exactly.

00:13:17.350 --> 00:13:18.690
On this trip to Simo's hometown,

00:13:19.110 --> 00:13:21.300
We saw that even ordinary people

00:13:21.320 --> 00:13:22.260
Were in panic

00:13:22.800 --> 00:13:23.450
Over the Sea Calamity.

00:13:24.580 --> 00:13:25.450
As cultivators,

00:13:26.110 --> 00:13:27.610
We should protect the people

00:13:27.960 --> 00:13:28.810
In times of crisis.

00:13:29.660 --> 00:13:30.540
During this Sea Calamity,

00:13:32.630 --> 00:13:34.020
We can't afford even a single mistake.

00:13:35.320 --> 00:13:37.020
Lu is guarding the mountain-sea barrier.

00:13:37.280 --> 00:13:38.180
If anything unusual happens,

00:13:38.200 --> 00:13:39.330
He'll send word soon.

00:13:41.040 --> 00:13:41.610
Gelin.

00:13:44.110 --> 00:13:45.380
I think

00:13:45.750 --> 00:13:47.970
Lu is a reliable man.

00:13:48.870 --> 00:13:50.090
I can rest easy

00:13:50.350 --> 00:13:51.900
Entrusting you to him.

00:13:52.080 --> 00:13:52.780
Changyue.

00:13:53.440 --> 00:13:54.060
Alright.

00:13:54.440 --> 00:13:55.300
I'll go check on Tongzhou,

00:13:55.750 --> 00:13:57.140
So that he won't overthink.

00:13:57.800 --> 00:13:58.420
Wait.

00:13:59.040 --> 00:13:59.970
I'll come with you.

00:14:00.830 --> 00:14:01.300
Alright.

00:14:01.660 --> 00:14:02.380
I'm leaving.

00:14:31.800 --> 00:14:33.140
Gelin and Changyue came to see you,

00:14:34.040 --> 00:14:34.900
But I sent them away.

00:14:35.830 --> 00:14:37.210
How long are you planning to keep me locked up?

00:14:38.990 --> 00:14:39.660
You want to leave?

00:14:42.200 --> 00:14:43.610
I have important things to do.

00:14:44.710 --> 00:14:45.810
If you're not going to kill me,

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:47.300
Then let me go.

00:14:47.990 --> 00:14:49.140
Ji Tongzhou, wake up.

00:14:50.560 --> 00:14:51.730
Xiuyuan needs us.

00:14:55.280 --> 00:14:56.380
Needs us?

00:14:57.080 --> 00:14:58.090
You're going to Lei Xiuyuan?

00:15:01.040 --> 00:15:02.300
Don't be so stubborn.

00:15:04.280 --> 00:15:05.570
I'm stubborn?

00:15:06.080 --> 00:15:07.300
What are you really trying to do?

00:15:09.440 --> 00:15:10.540
The Sea Calamity is coming.

00:15:10.920 --> 00:15:11.780
There's not much time.

00:15:12.320 --> 00:15:13.090
Let me out.

00:15:13.750 --> 00:15:15.260
Maybe I can stop it.

00:15:15.510 --> 00:15:16.300
Stop it?

00:15:17.280 --> 00:15:18.420
How?

00:15:19.510 --> 00:15:20.180
Lifei,

00:15:20.960 --> 00:15:22.380
You used to be better

00:15:22.400 --> 00:15:23.610
At lying than this.

00:15:24.040 --> 00:15:24.610
Tongzhou,

00:15:25.710 --> 00:15:26.780
The three of us have been through

00:15:26.800 --> 00:15:28.140
Life and death together for years.

00:15:28.510 --> 00:15:29.450
Trust me this once!

00:15:30.750 --> 00:15:31.940
Even if I trust you,

00:15:32.350 --> 00:15:33.060
What about everyone else?

00:15:34.040 --> 00:15:34.900
To them,

00:15:34.920 --> 00:15:35.970
You're just the Fruit of the Divine Tree.

00:15:36.080 --> 00:15:36.970
An anomaly!

00:15:37.800 --> 00:15:39.420
Only I see you as human.

00:15:40.320 --> 00:15:41.850
I've given you my all,

00:15:42.080 --> 00:15:43.330
Yet you just want to leave!

00:15:44.320 --> 00:15:45.210
You see me as human?

00:15:47.040 --> 00:15:48.210
Then why lock me up?

00:15:48.510 --> 00:15:49.850
I'm protecting you!

00:15:50.160 --> 00:15:50.970
Every immortal sect

00:15:50.990 --> 00:15:52.210
Is after your spirit power.

00:15:52.230 --> 00:15:53.660
Only I can protect you!

00:15:57.960 --> 00:15:59.260
Don't you want my spirit power?

00:16:02.440 --> 00:16:04.450
You still need a lot to break through

00:16:05.320 --> 00:16:06.940
The fifth level of Xuanhua Sacred Fire, don't you?

00:16:10.200 --> 00:16:13.810
Sometimes I wish I could live in ignorance.

00:16:15.870 --> 00:16:17.260
Because being clear-headed

00:16:18.710 --> 00:16:19.940
Hurts too much.

00:16:31.280 --> 00:16:32.060
What do you know?

00:16:35.630 --> 00:16:36.810
I wish I knew nothing.

00:16:39.750 --> 00:16:40.490
Yes.

00:16:41.230 --> 00:16:42.420
I do want your spirit power.

00:16:42.990 --> 00:16:44.780
Once I break through the fifth level,

00:16:45.040 --> 00:16:46.330
I'll be unstoppable!

00:16:46.870 --> 00:16:47.540
And then no one

00:16:47.560 --> 00:16:48.850
Will ever take you from me again!

00:16:52.160 --> 00:16:54.060
If you wanted spirit power, you could've just asked me.

00:16:55.080 --> 00:16:56.140
I would've given it to you.

00:16:58.560 --> 00:16:59.900
But you kept hiding

00:17:00.440 --> 00:17:01.450
And scheming.

00:17:02.870 --> 00:17:03.900
Because you know what you did

00:17:03.920 --> 00:17:04.970
Was wrong yourself.

00:17:06.080 --> 00:17:07.610
You just can't control it, can you?

00:17:07.960 --> 00:17:08.340
You!

00:17:12.230 --> 00:17:12.940
Fine.

00:17:13.510 --> 00:17:14.730
Then I'll just take it from you!

00:17:15.230 --> 00:17:16.210
Tongzhou, I'm sorry.

00:17:18.230 --> 00:17:19.290
I was wrong.

00:17:21.070 --> 00:17:22.530
I thought the bond between the three of us

00:17:23.400 --> 00:17:24.900
Was enough to see us through any crisis

00:17:26.270 --> 00:17:28.050
And help you let go of your obsession.

00:17:30.200 --> 00:17:31.340
But I found out

00:17:33.120 --> 00:17:35.050
It only fed your darker side.

00:17:39.960 --> 00:17:41.050
We hurt you.

00:17:42.840 --> 00:17:44.380
So whatever you do,

00:17:46.710 --> 00:17:47.730
I won't blame you.

00:17:50.470 --> 00:17:51.450
Jiang Lifei!

00:18:03.550 --> 00:18:04.420
Your Highness,

00:18:05.120 --> 00:18:06.580
Since you can't do it,

00:18:06.880 --> 00:18:09.450
How about I step in?

00:18:18.680 --> 00:18:19.690
Your cultivation

00:18:20.120 --> 00:18:21.380
Has grown fast in just a few days.

00:18:27.160 --> 00:18:29.210
You collected Cuixuan's body.

00:18:30.120 --> 00:18:31.250
Could it be that you...?

00:18:37.200 --> 00:18:39.660
He had demonic energy and spirit power.

00:18:40.470 --> 00:18:41.970
It'd be a waste

00:18:42.360 --> 00:18:43.690
To let it rot.

00:18:47.920 --> 00:18:49.250
You devoured your own master.

00:18:50.200 --> 00:18:51.580
You're insane.

00:18:52.310 --> 00:18:53.730
It seems both the immortal sects

00:18:54.680 --> 00:18:56.010
And demon clans have their share of scum!

00:18:58.680 --> 00:19:01.900
Jiang Lifei, no matter how sharp your tongue,

00:19:02.270 --> 00:19:05.250
No one's coming to save you this time.

00:19:16.440 --> 00:19:17.180
It was you.

00:19:18.990 --> 00:19:20.690
You killed Zhaomin!

00:19:34.070 --> 00:19:35.210
You animal!

00:19:36.160 --> 00:19:36.940
Why?

00:19:44.960 --> 00:19:45.860
Why?

00:19:46.470 --> 00:19:47.420
If I hadn't killed her,

00:19:48.200 --> 00:19:49.580
Would you have given up on Yecha?

00:19:50.880 --> 00:19:52.420
Would you have killed him yourself?

00:19:56.920 --> 00:19:58.050
What a pity.

00:19:58.710 --> 00:20:00.860
You two still have feelings for each other.

00:20:03.880 --> 00:20:05.730
Truly, those not of our kind

00:20:06.680 --> 00:20:07.900
Must be wiped out!

00:20:17.550 --> 00:20:18.140
Lifei.

00:20:28.550 --> 00:20:31.290
The Divine Tree's power is truly remarkable.

00:20:32.270 --> 00:20:33.140
Your Highness,

00:20:34.270 --> 00:20:36.140
Join me now.

00:20:36.710 --> 00:20:39.900
Together we'll rule the world.

00:20:43.880 --> 00:20:44.770
Fine.

00:21:14.880 --> 00:21:15.450
This is...?

00:21:22.990 --> 00:21:23.770
Your Highness.

00:21:33.360 --> 00:21:34.770
Dragon-Phoenix Sanctuary Pendant.

00:21:36.230 --> 00:21:37.820
Dragon and Phoenix, bound as one.

00:21:39.120 --> 00:21:40.380
If you absorb the Phoenix,

00:21:42.030 --> 00:21:44.010
The Dragon will turn on you.

00:21:46.120 --> 00:21:47.050
You're right.

00:21:48.200 --> 00:21:49.580
You have demonic energy and spirit power.

00:21:49.600 --> 00:21:50.900
It'd be a waste

00:21:52.550 --> 00:21:54.180
To let it rot.

00:21:57.230 --> 00:21:58.970
I worked so hard for this...

00:21:59.840 --> 00:22:01.730
I won't accept it!

00:22:06.680 --> 00:22:08.290
You should be honored to help me

00:22:09.270 --> 00:22:10.580
Achieve the Great Dao!

00:22:20.920 --> 00:22:21.730
Stop!

00:22:27.750 --> 00:22:29.140
If you don't stop, you'll fall to the demon!

00:22:30.400 --> 00:22:31.290
Stop!

00:22:31.310 --> 00:22:32.340
Tongzhou!

00:22:42.510 --> 00:22:44.450
You're crazy!

00:22:57.070 --> 00:22:57.940
I'm crazy?

00:23:00.510 --> 00:23:01.970
You drove me crazy!

00:23:03.360 --> 00:23:04.730
I did so much for you.

00:23:05.440 --> 00:23:06.860
Why do you treat me like this?

00:23:06.960 --> 00:23:07.970
Why?

00:23:13.360 --> 00:23:16.690
Tongzhou, let it go.

00:23:17.680 --> 00:23:18.380
Let it go?

00:23:21.710 --> 00:23:23.450
You all betrayed me.

00:23:24.200 --> 00:23:25.820
Why should I let any of you go?

00:23:26.840 --> 00:23:27.860
Why?

00:23:37.750 --> 00:23:38.450
Your Highness!

00:23:39.160 --> 00:23:39.940
What are you doing?

00:23:54.470 --> 00:23:55.250
What am I doing?

00:23:58.470 --> 00:23:58.940
I...

00:24:01.360 --> 00:24:01.770
I was...

00:24:01.990 --> 00:24:02.420
Your Highness.

00:24:02.750 --> 00:24:03.380
Get away!

00:24:10.160 --> 00:24:10.690
Your Highness!

00:24:34.400 --> 00:24:36.290
I've mastered the fifth level

00:24:37.360 --> 00:24:38.490
Of Xuanhua Sacred Fire!

00:24:41.440 --> 00:24:43.770
You just can't control it, can you?

00:24:51.640 --> 00:24:52.180
No.

00:24:53.400 --> 00:24:54.100
I'm not crazy.

00:24:56.400 --> 00:24:57.970
I just wanted to become stronger.

00:24:58.680 --> 00:24:59.490
What's wrong with that?

00:25:00.550 --> 00:25:01.420
What's wrong?

00:25:07.990 --> 00:25:08.940
Congratulations,

00:25:08.960 --> 00:25:10.290
Your Highness.

00:25:10.790 --> 00:25:12.900
Once you've fully absorbed the Divine Tree's power,

00:25:13.160 --> 00:25:14.340
Your cultivation will reach its peak.

00:25:14.680 --> 00:25:17.730
Don't forget to look out for me when that happens.

00:25:22.920 --> 00:25:24.380
Who do you think you are?

00:25:30.680 --> 00:25:31.420
Your Highness,

00:25:32.120 --> 00:25:33.940
Why pretend to be so noble?

00:25:34.200 --> 00:25:37.140
You're just like us.

00:25:43.230 --> 00:25:44.250
I am

00:25:45.790 --> 00:25:46.820
Not like you.

00:25:47.270 --> 00:25:48.180
Yes, you are.

00:25:50.640 --> 00:25:52.380
I just saw you absorbing...

00:26:20.710 --> 00:26:21.420
Tongzhou.

00:26:22.070 --> 00:26:22.450
What...

00:26:25.200 --> 00:26:26.140
What were you doing?

00:26:29.640 --> 00:26:30.340
Are you crazy?

00:26:31.270 --> 00:26:32.530
You're even draining Lifei?

00:26:34.440 --> 00:26:34.970
I'm not crazy.

00:26:36.640 --> 00:26:37.180
I'm not crazy!

00:26:39.270 --> 00:26:39.820
Tongzhou,

00:26:40.840 --> 00:26:41.340
Don't you remember?

00:26:42.310 --> 00:26:43.380
We promised

00:26:43.840 --> 00:26:45.140
- Yeah. - to go through life and death together.

00:26:46.710 --> 00:26:48.210
Stop now, Tongzhou!

00:26:49.070 --> 00:26:50.010
Yes, Tongzhou.

00:26:50.440 --> 00:26:51.420
Xiuyuan is the Demon Lord.

00:26:51.880 --> 00:26:53.050
Maybe that's not a bad thing.

00:26:53.990 --> 00:26:55.860
Perhaps it could change the relationship

00:26:56.510 --> 00:26:57.730
Between the two clans.

00:26:59.030 --> 00:27:00.250
Xiuyuan again.

00:27:01.200 --> 00:27:02.340
Always Xiuyuan!

00:27:03.920 --> 00:27:04.940
Tongzhou, stop!

00:27:04.960 --> 00:27:06.380
- Tongzhou. - Snap out of it!

00:27:06.640 --> 00:27:07.970
- Tongzhou. - Wake up, Tongzhou!

00:27:08.400 --> 00:27:08.900
Tongzhou!

00:27:09.120 --> 00:27:09.490
Tongzhou.

00:27:09.510 --> 00:27:10.420
Don't you trust Xiuyuan?

00:27:10.440 --> 00:27:10.820
Tongzhou.

00:27:10.840 --> 00:27:12.250
Xiuyuan is one of us!

00:27:14.600 --> 00:27:15.050
Tongzhou?

00:27:15.360 --> 00:27:15.820
Ye.

00:27:16.160 --> 00:27:16.900
Tongzhou, what's wrong with you?

00:27:17.230 --> 00:27:17.940
Something's off with him.

00:27:18.200 --> 00:27:18.690
Go!

00:27:18.710 --> 00:27:19.820
Tongzhou, wake up!

00:27:19.840 --> 00:27:20.580
Come on, Ye!

00:27:22.990 --> 00:27:23.660
Go!

00:27:24.310 --> 00:27:24.970
Tongzhou!

00:27:24.990 --> 00:27:26.420
Destroy it all!

00:27:51.310 --> 00:27:51.900
Tongzhou!

00:27:52.310 --> 00:27:53.010
Tongzhou!

00:27:54.640 --> 00:27:55.770
Tongzhou, no!

00:28:47.630 --> 00:28:50.030
♪The warmth within my arms♪

00:28:50.030 --> 00:28:50.580
Tongzhou.

00:28:51.230 --> 00:28:52.380
Just an illusion.

00:28:53.030 --> 00:28:53.820
None of it was real.

00:28:55.040 --> 00:28:57.640
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

00:28:57.640 --> 00:28:58.290
All fake.

00:28:59.920 --> 00:29:00.660
It must be a dream.

00:29:00.660 --> 00:29:02.070
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

00:29:02.920 --> 00:29:03.580
None of it was real.

00:29:03.580 --> 00:29:04.880
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

00:29:04.880 --> 00:29:05.770
It must be fake.

00:29:05.960 --> 00:29:09.160
♪I can no longer tell you♪

00:29:09.560 --> 00:29:12.760
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

00:29:13.040 --> 00:29:16.080
♪Utter that line♪

00:29:16.440 --> 00:29:18.160
♪Knowing love and hate♪

00:29:18.480 --> 00:29:22.400
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

00:29:24.710 --> 00:29:25.660
Don't pour anymore.

00:29:25.790 --> 00:29:26.940
Alright, Gelin.

00:29:27.310 --> 00:29:29.450
We'll never be apart!

00:29:30.360 --> 00:29:34.720
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

00:29:35.000 --> 00:29:37.960
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

00:29:38.280 --> 00:29:39.990
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

00:29:39.990 --> 00:29:42.620
In three years, the once-in-five-centuries Sea Calamity will come.

00:29:43.230 --> 00:29:45.340
We'll gather again at Lugong Town

00:29:45.680 --> 00:29:46.450
To stand against it together.

00:29:47.200 --> 00:29:48.420
That would make our bond worthwhile.

00:29:48.440 --> 00:29:49.050
Well said.

00:29:49.050 --> 00:29:51.480
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

00:29:52.840 --> 00:29:54.480
♪You're still screaming♪

00:29:54.760 --> 00:29:57.840
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

00:29:57.840 --> 00:29:58.250
No.

00:29:59.550 --> 00:30:00.290
No! Ye Ye.

00:30:00.290 --> 00:30:02.550
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

00:30:02.550 --> 00:30:03.340
I... I didn't kill you.

00:30:04.550 --> 00:30:05.290
I didn't kill you!

00:30:05.290 --> 00:30:06.960
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

00:30:07.270 --> 00:30:11.230
♪Leaping straight into that heartbreaking past♪

00:30:11.230 --> 00:30:11.770
I'm sorry.

00:30:12.600 --> 00:30:13.250
Sorry.

00:30:14.790 --> 00:30:15.450
I'm sorry.

00:30:15.480 --> 00:30:18.120
♪Just to keep you safe♪

00:30:29.610 --> 00:30:31.120
♪My breath is about to stop♪

00:30:31.120 --> 00:30:33.050
I'm so sorry.

00:30:33.340 --> 00:30:36.560
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

00:30:36.700 --> 00:30:39.900
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

00:30:40.180 --> 00:30:43.220
♪To light your way through the night♪

00:30:43.840 --> 00:30:44.380
Your Highness.

00:30:45.120 --> 00:30:45.690
Stop.

00:30:46.030 --> 00:30:46.660
Stop thinking about it.

00:30:46.920 --> 00:30:47.620
Please.

00:30:49.070 --> 00:30:49.530
I didn't kill you.

00:30:49.550 --> 00:30:51.180
Your Highness, stop thinking about it!

00:30:51.200 --> 00:30:52.010
Stop!

00:30:52.470 --> 00:30:53.290
Your Highness!

00:30:53.290 --> 00:30:57.100
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

00:30:57.480 --> 00:31:01.810
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

00:31:02.170 --> 00:31:05.010
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

00:31:05.330 --> 00:31:07.490
♪I'd shatter my soul♪

00:31:07.890 --> 00:31:12.400
♪To lay all your days in peace♪

00:31:12.400 --> 00:31:13.050
Lifei?

00:31:13.050 --> 00:31:14.450
♪Who says that love and hate♪

00:31:14.600 --> 00:31:16.050
Lifei, I didn't kill them.

00:31:16.470 --> 00:31:17.050
Believe me.

00:31:17.360 --> 00:31:18.580
Lifei, I didn't kill Ye Ye.

00:31:19.550 --> 00:31:20.180
I was wrong.

00:31:20.470 --> 00:31:21.010
I'm sorry.

00:31:21.160 --> 00:31:21.690
Forgive me.

00:31:21.710 --> 00:31:22.380
- Forgive me. - I know.

00:31:22.640 --> 00:31:23.290
I know.

00:31:23.400 --> 00:31:24.210
It's not your fault.

00:31:24.510 --> 00:31:25.050
Get up.

00:31:25.640 --> 00:31:26.970
No! No.

00:31:27.640 --> 00:31:28.420
Don't leave me.

00:31:28.420 --> 00:31:30.970
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

00:31:31.510 --> 00:31:32.730
No, Lifei.

00:31:32.960 --> 00:31:34.140
Don't leave me.

00:31:34.530 --> 00:31:39.400
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

00:31:39.400 --> 00:31:40.660
I won't leave you.

00:31:41.330 --> 00:31:44.890
♪To wander with you♪

00:31:46.030 --> 00:31:46.770
Lifei.

00:31:47.750 --> 00:31:48.900
Lifei.

00:31:51.120 --> 00:31:51.770
Lu!

00:31:52.070 --> 00:31:52.530
Gelin.

00:31:52.920 --> 00:31:54.100
Changyue and Ye are gone.

00:31:54.470 --> 00:31:55.420
I looked for them all night,

00:31:55.440 --> 00:31:56.380
But they're nowhere.

00:31:57.070 --> 00:31:58.690
They didn't come back to their room last night.

00:31:58.960 --> 00:32:00.250
Last night, strange phenomena occurred in the East Sea.

00:32:00.510 --> 00:32:01.450
Dark clouds filled the sky.

00:32:01.750 --> 00:32:03.770
I rushed back to Duanming City to reinforce the defensive formation.

00:32:04.120 --> 00:32:05.290
All the immortal sects sent people

00:32:05.440 --> 00:32:06.250
To patrol the coast,

00:32:06.470 --> 00:32:07.380
Including Dizang Sect.

00:32:07.960 --> 00:32:10.140
Maybe Ye Ye and Changyue went to help.

00:32:15.510 --> 00:32:16.250
- What's wrong? - What's happening?

00:32:21.270 --> 00:32:22.290
The city wall is collapsing, Lu.

00:32:29.160 --> 00:32:29.770
- Mr. Mo? - Mr. Mo?

00:32:30.310 --> 00:32:32.420
The Sea Calamity is coming! Go guard the mountain-sea barrier!

00:32:56.400 --> 00:32:57.210
You're trying to escape?

00:32:57.960 --> 00:32:58.530
There's no time!

00:32:58.990 --> 00:32:59.900
Let me out!

00:33:00.600 --> 00:33:02.490
Jiang Lifei, you still don't understand me?

00:33:03.270 --> 00:33:04.380
After all I've done for you,

00:33:04.920 --> 00:33:06.140
You still want to go to Lei Xiuyuan?

00:33:23.840 --> 00:33:25.580
Zhurong Fire severs the meridians and the veins.

00:33:26.120 --> 00:33:27.530
Your limbs are crippled now.

00:33:27.960 --> 00:33:28.770
How can you leave?

00:33:29.360 --> 00:33:30.050
There's no time.

00:33:31.550 --> 00:33:32.140
Tongzhou.

00:33:33.510 --> 00:33:34.660
You'll regret this!

00:33:35.550 --> 00:33:37.140
Just stay put.

00:33:37.790 --> 00:33:38.530
Don't go anywhere.

00:33:39.840 --> 00:33:40.450
Tongzhou!

00:34:57.550 --> 00:34:59.010
So the way back across the sea

00:34:59.670 --> 00:35:00.530
Lies within Guixu.

00:35:19.960 --> 00:35:20.610
What is it?

00:35:29.110 --> 00:35:30.450
Guixu can devour the heavens

00:35:31.240 --> 00:35:32.130
And has countless dark spirits.

00:35:39.960 --> 00:35:40.570
Dark spirits?

00:36:01.990 --> 00:36:02.530
Mr. Mo,

00:36:02.990 --> 00:36:03.940
What will the Sea Calamity be like?

00:36:04.800 --> 00:36:05.570
First tsunamis,

00:36:06.760 --> 00:36:07.860
Then thunder and fire,

00:36:09.670 --> 00:36:10.170
Then

00:36:11.800 --> 00:36:12.420
The end of the world.

00:36:25.550 --> 00:36:26.380
Hold on, everyone!

00:36:36.320 --> 00:36:37.530
Coward.

00:36:39.470 --> 00:36:40.650
Why didn't Changyue and Ye come?

00:37:11.150 --> 00:37:11.900
Tongzhou?

00:37:12.880 --> 00:37:14.490
Where did he get such boundless spirit power?

00:37:15.670 --> 00:37:16.570
It's Prince Ying!

00:37:16.880 --> 00:37:17.820
Help now!

00:37:24.360 --> 00:37:25.900
Ji Tongzhou must have taken the Divine Tree's power

00:37:26.280 --> 00:37:27.570
To become so strong.

00:37:40.030 --> 00:37:40.530
What are you doing?

00:37:50.240 --> 00:37:51.010
Sect Leader Miao.

00:37:52.920 --> 00:37:54.260
Instead of holding back the Sea Calamity,

00:37:55.030 --> 00:37:56.650
You're here to devour my spirit power?

00:37:57.760 --> 00:37:59.130
Once I absorb the Divine Tree's power,

00:37:59.510 --> 00:38:00.570
I'll hold back the Sea Calamity.

00:38:00.960 --> 00:38:03.010
Consider it a sacrifice for the world!

00:38:13.720 --> 00:38:14.260
Mr. Zhu?

00:38:17.400 --> 00:38:18.260
And me!

00:38:20.280 --> 00:38:20.970
Sect Leader Miao,

00:38:21.360 --> 00:38:22.380
With the calamity upon us,

00:38:22.670 --> 00:38:25.940
Dizang Sect abandons the battlefield to take advantage.

00:38:26.320 --> 00:38:27.090
Word of this

00:38:27.470 --> 00:38:29.900
Will disgrace your sect.

00:38:30.440 --> 00:38:32.900
I was afraid the demons might attack.

00:38:33.510 --> 00:38:34.220
So I came to check.

00:38:34.880 --> 00:38:35.780
Since you two are here,

00:38:36.320 --> 00:38:38.170
I'll go help defend the barrier.

00:39:44.110 --> 00:39:44.650
My Lord.

00:39:51.070 --> 00:39:52.530
My Lord, we'll help you.

00:40:07.440 --> 00:40:07.970
Rakshasa!

00:40:09.150 --> 00:40:09.570
Qiongqi!

00:40:55.840 --> 00:40:56.740
Look. Look over there.

00:40:57.440 --> 00:40:58.570
Home!

00:40:58.960 --> 00:41:00.380
Yes.

00:41:00.400 --> 00:41:01.260
- My Lord. - We can go back!

00:41:01.280 --> 00:41:02.300
We can go home!

00:41:02.760 --> 00:41:03.610
Finally going home!

00:41:03.630 --> 00:41:04.820
We can finally go back!

00:41:05.920 --> 00:41:06.900
Going home!

00:41:07.880 --> 00:41:08.740
Wonderful!

00:41:10.670 --> 00:41:11.420
Take our people

00:41:13.150 --> 00:41:13.780
Home!

00:41:14.960 --> 00:41:17.610
Thank you, My Lord!

00:41:39.240 --> 00:41:40.530
Take a rest. Let me take over.

00:41:42.360 --> 00:41:42.740
Here.

00:41:53.440 --> 00:41:54.010
Sir.

00:42:03.630 --> 00:42:05.650
How is Miss Jiang?

00:42:07.550 --> 00:42:09.530
She was wounded by the fire blade of Zhurong Stone.

00:42:10.070 --> 00:42:11.220
Her meridians are destroyed.

00:42:11.760 --> 00:42:13.740
A massive infusion of spirit energy

00:42:14.470 --> 00:42:17.340
Might be her only chance.

00:42:30.110 --> 00:42:31.010
